{"tid":2265503,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"馬克龍赴尼斯悼教堂死者  法反恐警告升至最高級別","createTime":"2020-10-31T13:20:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T14:22:03.000Z","uid":25558,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7c21f63dad7635d5d7538966f369b1c448b38aba","tid":2265503,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:20:59.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201031/YH3BIY5YURCVZIWWK64ZBIJR6U/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201031%2FYH3BIY5YURCVZIWWK64ZBIJR6U%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak2WYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=9cd49e94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201031%2FYH3BIY5YURCVZIWWK64ZBIJR6U%2F&h=baeb1655\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201031/YH3BIY5YURCVZIWWK64ZBIJR6U/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n馬克龍赴尼斯悼教堂死者 <br />\n法反恐警告升至最高級別<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/EU3Wo7MN7uIXZJ3JPUGpSPPONwE=/806x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/VLMJOXGLXNEIFFX2VO5XOJFEBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FEU3Wo7MN7uIXZJ3JPUGpSPPONwE%3D%2F806x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FVLMJOXGLXNEIFFX2VO5XOJFEBA.jpg&h=8ff5aa0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■尼斯聖母聖殿前天下午響鐘悼念遇襲死者，武裝警察在外把守。<br />\n<br />\n法國前日再有極端伊斯蘭分子割頭施襲，半個月內第二宗；正值明天（11月1日）是天主教諸聖節，法國政府嚴防恐怖分子乘機施襲，將全國反恐警告提升到最高的「緊急」級別，趕赴尼斯追悼死者的總統馬克龍加派巡邏反恐軍力至7,000人，堅持不放棄國家核心價值。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：馬哈蒂爾：穆斯林有權殺數百萬法人<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Ykmn3Siepw7JvxsTLp_xiFErHO8=/1772x1181/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/64RDWGL5AZDW3NPDVPG2EHMPYM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FYkmn3Siepw7JvxsTLp_xiFErHO8%3D%2F1772x1181%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F64RDWGL5AZDW3NPDVPG2EHMPYM.jpg&h=9d30f520&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■馬克龍（前）前天到訪尼斯，強調不放棄法國核心價值。<br />\n<br />\n根據法國反恐檢察部門及警方資料，尼斯案刀手是21歲突尼斯男子奧薩維（Brahim Aouissaoui）；突尼斯政府。。。。。。。。。。。。&hellip;。。意政府審查一天後，確認奧薩維無刑事紀錄，亦不曾偷渡入境，但不符資格居留，卻未遞解他出境，只在翌日通知他要七天內離開，就此放虎歸山。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n曾在家鄉涉持刀案被捕<br />\n<br />\n突尼斯政府說奧薩維2016年曾因持刀暴力案被捕。奧薩維曾向人提過想到法國，當局相信他是在意國獲釋後一、兩天便乘火車入巴黎，。。。。。。。。。。。。。。9時10分才被到場警員連開14槍傷制服，傷勢危殆。警方至前晚再拘留一名47歲男子，疑與刀手過從甚密。<br />\n<br />\n奧薩維於突尼斯的家人昨得悉他成為殺人兇手大感震驚，其母淚流滿面說，早前兒子致電說抵達法國時已感奇怪，反問：「你不懂法語，又舉目無親，孤身一人，幹麼要去那裏呢？」其兄則說弟弟到法國後一直有聯絡，前日早上還傳了聖殿照片給他。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聖殿職員遭割喉遺兩子<br />\n<br />\n法國當局又披露三名死者身份和背景，慘被兇手割頭的是60歲女教友，55歲聖。。。。。。。。。。。。。。拜託救護車人員轉告遺言：「跟我的孩子說：我愛他們。」其後附近店家亦接到生還者求助，代為報警。<br />\n<br />\n內政部長達爾馬寧昨日在電台說，法國正迎戰內外夾擊的極端伊斯蘭主義，會成為主要目標是因為國家象徵自由、世俗主義和法治，「民眾要有心理準備，國內恐怖襲擊或陸續有來」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/美聯社/英國《每日郵報》"},{"pid":"e5b3d55334b69b76a5135cee9c7acbd9bef734d7","tid":2265503,"uid":1672,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:29:55.000Z","msg":"趕班巴基躝坦出歐洲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd95f4745b438ce7edb95403b3265040004915b2","tid":2265503,"uid":274435,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:33:18.000Z","msg":"送返班撚屌返去沙漠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06cb8aa58eba8d90cc190e30f7516c57c8b62015","tid":2265503,"uid":55941,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T13:38:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />說好的大愛呢 <br />\n<br />\n咪被人斬多兩三件<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/read.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早就要趕班友出法國"},{"pid":"d3124bdbeb1ab6746be38e958d51405fd0e6d16b","tid":2265503,"uid